text: Georg Konermann (born 24 June 1960) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Rheine
